  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nPresently we manually implement `TestRandom` on all types.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/a1118e13ae1279d9bfcc7e4a9faff5a55da2507d/eth2/types/src/attestation.rs#L73-L82\r\n\r\nThis is a prime target for a procedural derive macro, like implemented in #242.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n- Create a `test_random_derive` library crate in `eth2/utils`, using `eth2/utils/ssz_derive` as inspiration.\r\n- Add a `#[derive(TestRandom)]` macro in the `test_random_derive` crate.\r\n- Replace manual implementations with the derive wherever possible.\r\n\r\n~~(Note: `ssz_derive` is presently a PR in #242 and not in master)~~",
